main event: An unidentified object was reported in Sisaket Province, Thailand, on May 25, 1965, and identified as a Scout Rocket.
interesting points: The Royal Thai Government expressed concern for the unidentified object that fell from the sky., The object was launched from Mullion Island on December 16, 1964., The object was identified as being part of the igniting mechanism of a US Rocket., No eyewitness reports were available regarding the object., The object was analyzed to likely be a result of components from a Scout vehicle.
